            <h2>Applying for library card</h2>
            
            <p>You can get a library card from all Kyyti libraries by presenting a photo ID. If you are under 15 years old, you also need parental consent. You can print 
            the <a href="<?= $this->fileSrc('ilmoittautumislomake_eng_2024.pdf')?>" target="blank">Application Form for a Library Card</a> and fill it out before your visit.
            You can also get forms at the library.</p>
            <p>You can use your library card at all Kyyti libraries, which include all libraries in Kymenlaakso and Iitti.</p> 
            <p>The library card is free, but there is a fee for replacing a lost card. 
