                <li>Access e-resources</li>
                <li>Use any self-service library of the Kyyti network</li>
                <li>Use self-service machines for borrowing items</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You can obtain the PIN code from any Kyyti library. Please bring your library card and a photo ID. The PIN code will not be provided over the phone or via email.</p>

            <h3>Keep Your Contact Information Up to Date</h3>
            <p>If your name, address, or other contact information changes, please inform the library.
