            <p>You can order a reminder for approaching due dates via email or text message from the <a href="https://kyyti.finna.fi/MyResearch/Profile" target="blank">"Your Account" section</a> of the online library or by contacting the library. The service is free of charge.</p>
            
            <p>However, please note that you are responsible for any late fees even if the reminders do not reach you.</p>
            
            <h3>Renewing your loans</h3>
