            <h2>Kyyti libraries and opening hours</h2>
            
            <p>The libraries of Kymenlaakso and Iitti together form the Kyyti library network. The network's libraries share a common collection, reservation queue, and electronic resources.
            With your local municipality's library card, you can borrow materials from any library within the network and return the items to any Kyyti library. 
            If the material you are looking for is in the collection of another Kyyti library, you can request it free of charge to be delivered to your local library by placing a reservation on it.</p>
            
            <p>The Kyyti libraries consist of the following:</p>
            <ul class="list-bullets">
              <li>The city library of Hamina</li>
              <li>The municipal library of Iitti</li>          
              <li>The city library of Kotka</li>
