              <li>The municipal library of Miehikkälä</li>
              <li>The municipal library of Pyhtää</li>
              <li>The municipal library of Virolahti</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The library buses operate in Hamina, Iitti, Kotka, Kouvola, and Pyhtää.</p>
            
